    "description": "本課程主要是站在「公司管理者」的角度，利用相關財務理論來執行正確的財務決策，以追求公司價值極大化。學生可辨識與分析日常工作所面臨的問題，並運用所學財務技術來進行決策以解決其問題。<br>By introducing financial theories and practices, this course is to help corporation management making appropriate financial decisions to maximize the corporate market value. Students are able to identify and analyze the financial issues happening in their daily works, and apply the techniques to make appropriate decisions to solve their problems.",
